name: Rachna Dayal
title: Moderator
bio: Founder & Managing Partner at Sugati Ventures, and a venture capitalist and angel investor focused on HealthTech and AI. She brings global experience in corporate strategy, operations, and launching disruptive technologies.

name: Pras Hanuma
title: Panelist
bio: Venture Partner at NextUnicorn.Fund with extensive experience in early-stage investing and startup ecosystem development. He has been instrumental in supporting numerous successful startups across various sectors.

name: Nicholas Mohnacky
title: Panelist
bio: Co-founder and CEO of bundlelQ, a platform revolutionizing how businesses manage and optimize their operations. With a background in technology and entrepreneurship, Nicholas brings innovative perspectives to the panel discussion.

name: Hans Sandhu
title: Panelist
bio: Serial entrepreneur and investor with a passion for building transformative technology companies. Hans has founded and scaled multiple startups, bringing deep operational expertise to the discussion on the future of business with AI.
